text: The franc (French, ) was the currency of Tunisia from 1891 to 1958. 100 centimes (صنتيم) made one Tunisian franc. The currency was worth the same amount as the French franc. ==References== * * Category:19th-century establishments in Tunisia Category:1891 establishments Category:1960 disestablishments in Africa Category:History of Tunisia Category:Currency of Africa
title: Tunisian franc
